OL,3,C'Significant Concern': Minister Steve
OL,4,CLuce to regulate cannabis prescriptions
OL,6,FConcerns have been raised after
OL,7,Fmedicinal cannabis prescription rates
OL,8,Fin Jersey were found to be 120 times
OL,9,Fhigher than in England.
OL,11,FHealth Minister Tom Binet and
OL,12,FEnvironment Minister Steve Luce say
OL,13,Fthey plan to introduce new regulations
OL,14,Fto address the issue.
OL,16,FIt comes after an audit revealed the
OL,17,Fdifference between Jersey and England
OL,18,Fand suggested amounts may not align
OL,19,Fwith NICE or NHS guidelines.
