OL,3,C'Significant Concern': Minister Steve
OL,4,CLuce to regulate cannabis prescriptions
OL,6,FMinister Tom Binet says: "We will have
OL,7,Fto do something to tidy it up a little
OL,8,Fand be more sure about how much is
OL,9,Fbeing prescribed and how people use
OL,10,Fit."
OL,12,FThe audit revealed that 6.08% of
OL,13,FJersey's working population has a
OL,14,Fprescription for medicinal cannabis,
OL,15,Fcompared to 0.05% in England.
OL,17,FThe audit suggests that some people
OL,18,Fmay have gone against the guidelines
OL,19,Fby receiving more than they were
OL,20,Fprescribed monthly.
