OL,3,C'Significant Concern': Minister Steve
OL,4,CLuce to regulate cannabis prescriptions
OL,6,FIn response, Deputy Steve Luce,
OL,7,FMinister for the Environment said:
OL,8,F"The differences in the levels of
OL,9,Fprescribing of medicinal cannabis that
OL,10,Fis taking place in Jersey when
OL,11,Fcompared with England is significant.
OL,13,F"The audit also suggests that some
OL,14,Fpeople are receiving multiple
OL,15,Fprescriptions at levels which may be
OL,16,Fharmful to their health, this is of
OL,17,Fsignificant concern. I am committed to
OL,18,Fdeveloping the legislation necessary
OL,19,Fto regulate and inspect cannabis
OL,20,Fclinics in Jersey."
